Description: The ancient art of Archery allows you to use a Bow and Arrow to great effect.  This power set has an inherent bonus to Accuracy.

Powers.DescLong: A quick attack that fires an arrow at your foe after only minimal aiming. Fast, but little damage. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Fast
Though it takes longer to execute, your Aimed Shot deals greater damage than Snap Shot. Damage: High, Recharge: Moderate
You fire a fistful of arrows at foes in a cone in front of you. Good at close range. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Moderate
You fire a blunt, weighted arrow at your target's chest. The Stunning Shot inflicts high damage and has a good chance of stunning your foe. Damage: High, Recharge: Slow
Greatly increases the chance to hit of your attacks for a few seconds. Slightly increases damage and range. Recharge: Long
You fire a grenade-tipped arrow at long range. This explosion affects all within the blast radius, and can knock them back. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Slow
You fire a Blazing Arrow at your foe, dealing some Lethal damage and causing them to catch on fire and burn. Damage: High, Recharge: Slow
A perfectly aimed and fast shot that blasts your foes. Damage: Very High, Recharge: Slow
You unleash a Rain of Arrows on a targeted location, damaging foes within a large area. Damage: Extreme (DoT), Recharge: Long
